headline: Is Synopsys (SNPS) a Buy as Wall Street Analysts Look Optimistic?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Synopsys (SNPS) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?

headline: Taiwan Semiconductor Unveils Ultra-Advanced Chip Tech
summary: Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Co. (NYSE: TSM) shares were trending on Thursday as the company showcased its new A14, or 1.4nm, logic process technology at its North America Technology Symposium in Santa Clara, California. TSM is a key supplier to industry giants like Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) and Apple (NASDAQ: AAPL), and the unveiling of its next-generation technology highlights its central role in the ongoing artificial intelligence (AI) boom.
